in your organization.

244
00:14:14,100 --> 00:14:17,760
And then declarative policies
are also very powerful.

245
00:14:17,760 --> 00:14:22,760
Here, they enforce a desired
configuration for a resource,

246
00:14:24,450 --> 00:14:29,190
and those resources
include VPC, EC2 and EBS.

247
00:14:29,190 --> 00:14:34,190
But again, the power here is
that this is applied at scale.

248
00:14:39,540 --> 00:14:44,103
Now, AWS Config rules, these
are our detective controls.

249
00:14:47,730 --> 00:14:51,450
I think the main points I'd
