00:15:22,500 --> 00:15:26,310
but you can also create
custom Config aggregators

259
00:15:26,310 --> 00:15:31,310
for your own special accounts or regions.

260
00:15:33,030 --> 00:15:35,403
And then custom rules.

261
00:15:37,560 --> 00:15:38,940
You can build custom rules

262
00:15:38,940 --> 00:15:41,340
depending on what your
business requirements are.

